englishTranslation: At 10:15 by the pool we have gymnastics

hebrewFromSub: לאחר מכן במרפסת המערבית יש לנו סימפוזיון עם הרב מאירק שרמן  על פסכולוגית העלבת קומיקאים
englishFromSub: Then on the west porch we have a symposium by Rabbi Maurice Sherman  on the psychology of insult comedians
englishTranslation: Then on the West Terrace we have a symposium with Rabbi Meirk Sherman on the insult of comedians

hebrewFromSub: לכן אני אומר "אל תשאל מה המלצר יכול לעשות למענך  אלא מה אתה יכול לעשות למען המלצר"
englishFromSub: So I say ""Ask not what your waiter can do for you  but what you can do for your waiter ""
englishTranslation: So I say "do not ask what the waiter can do for you but what you can do for the waiter"

hebrewFromSub: אם הטיפים ימשיכו אז יש לי מספיק בשביל האלפא רומאו שלי
englishFromSub: If tips keep up I'll have enough for my Alfa Romeo
englishTranslation: If the tips continue then I have enough for my Alfa Romeo
Ladies you guys look very nice

englishFromSub: Baby would you cover for me tonight
Tell Mom and Dad I went to lie down
englishTranslation: Tell Mom and Dad I went to bed

hebrewFromSub: יש שם נוף יפה מהתלולית הראשונה
englishFromSub: There's a pretty view from the first tee
englishTranslation: There is a beautiful view from the first mound

englishFromSub: I think you're a wonderful dancer
englishTranslation: I think you're a great dancer

hebrewFromSub: נו אמא שלי בעטה אותי החוצה כשהייתי בן 16
englishFromSub: Well my mother kicked me out when I was 16
englishTranslation: Well my mom kicked me out when I was 16
I've been a dancer ever since

hebrewFromSub: זאת העבודה היחידה שבאמת רציתי לעשות
englishFromSub: It's the only thing I ever wanted to do anyway
englishTranslation: This is the only job I really wanted to do

hebrewFromSub: נכון ששעורי הריקוד שלי מתחילים להשתלם
englishFromSub: Aren't my dance lessons starting to pay off
englishTranslation: It's true that my dance lessons are starting to pay off
